pengu.messenger

Class PenguMessengerClient.ContactItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • pengu.messenger.PenguMessengerClient.ContactItem
  • Enclosing class:
    PenguMessengerClient

    public static class PenguMessengerClient.ContactItem
extends java.lang.Object
    This class allows for contact objects to be created so that contacts information can be stored in an array. It stores details about a contact: the user ID, the username, the display/friendly name, the contact group, the contact group color, additional information, the public key and the expiry date of the public key.
